{"id":375108,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/12/【网络民议】恪尽职守，望风披靡/","date":"2014-12-19T02:40:19Z","modified":"2015-03-19T22:15:12Z","title":"【网络民议】恪尽职守，望风披靡","content":"<div class=\"pf_photo\">\n<p class=\"photo_wrap\"><img class=\"photo\" src=\"http://tp2.sinaimg.cn/1222601781/180/5660750347/1\" alt=\"骆新\" /></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pf_username\"><span class=\"username\">骆新</span> 东方卫视主持人兼新闻评论员</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/12/Screen-Shot-2014-12-18-at-6.26.19-PM.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-375110\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/12/Screen-Shot-2014-12-18-at-6.26.19-PM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2014-12-18 at 6.26.19 PM\" width=\"599\" height=\"391\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/12/Screen-Shot-2014-12-18-at-6.26.19-PM.png 1210w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/12/Screen-Shot-2014-12-18-at-6.26.19-PM-300x195.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/12/Screen-Shot-2014-12-18-at-6.26.19-PM-1024x668.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/12/Screen-Shot-2014-12-18-at-6.26.19-PM-230x150.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 599px) 100vw, 599px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下评论由数字时代编辑选自新浪微博：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1432857082\" target=\"_blank\">钻石之黎明</a>：望风披靡不就是丢盔卸甲逃命要紧的意思么？我是语文没学好吗？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/lbtgs\" target=\"_blank\">张洲</a>：我操，披了个靡的。望风而逃。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2095000577\" target=\"_blank\">第六星云</a>：按道理应当是所向披靡，搞到望风披靡，意思全拧。就差抱头鼠窜了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2023050737\" target=\"_blank\">云南杨明菊</a>：望风披靡？指的是徐家军谷家军？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/Jackysong1573\" target=\"_blank\">候鸟的天空1314</a>：打得赢就打，打不赢就跑<img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /><img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/liuaxiu\" target=\"_blank\">-Left-</a>：翻译：时刻保持警惕观察，发现不对就快跑。（被子军好辛苦）</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1855816910\" target=\"_blank\">xin-yue-</a>：说的是实话啊！敌人来了赶紧跑！请问:绿卡办好了吗？家里有几吨？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1669563382\" target=\"_blank\">Victor说</a>：领导见识深远，老奸巨猾，目不识丁<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">@人民日报</a> <a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">@央视新闻</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/cuizhu505\" target=\"_blank\">围观群众N</a>：维稳恪尽职守，民众望风披靡，有啥不对<img title=\"[熊猫]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6e/panda_org.gif\" alt=\"[熊猫]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2573687642\" target=\"_blank\">靖川旗长安</a>：秘书望风，领导披着衣服正在糜烂<img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/3089908093\" target=\"_blank\">竹人寸-</a>：→_→敌人已经被我军打得破釜沉舟，在我军绝对性的数量优势面前敌人已经以一当十→_→</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/wonengxing\" target=\"_blank\">当红-明月</a>：要不<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E8%8A%B1%E5%8D%83%E8%8A%B3?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">@花千芳</a> 们都能进皇宫。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1431354560\" target=\"_blank\">独关风月</a>：萱萱姑娘的文采，真是罄竹难书啊！<img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2263547664\" target=\"_blank\">追风筝的潜水员</a>：解放军看了也要生不如死！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2563796183\" target=\"_blank\">不要问我从哪里来2014</a>：就是牛逼，就是有自信</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2993800180\" target=\"_blank\">应该宠辱不惊</a>：别人都进了作协领导班子，自然没有时间和你们打嘴仗了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2810669031\" target=\"_blank\">花鲜草</a>：这得是经过多少道审批的结果呀!看来都是混是的。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/3243688702\" target=\"_blank\">焦虑的seagull</a>：说得没错啊，说假话你们要吐槽说真话你们又不爱听。<img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2301601637\" target=\"_blank\">徐德军律师</a>：宣萱对军队战斗力了如指掌</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/terrybolideforever\" target=\"_blank\">晚风-Terrence</a>：在国民党反动派消极抵抗之时, 我军早已望风披靡. 符合史实, 请问用于现代宣传标语有何不妥</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/xiaotidazuo\" target=\"_blank\">小题大作</a>：泄露国家机密！//<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E5%96%B7%E5%9A%8F%E7%BD%91%E9%93%82%E7%A8%8B?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">@喷嚏网铂程</a>: //<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E6%B4%8B%E8%91%B1%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E7%A4%BE?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">@洋葱日报社</a>: 谁写的，速来我们贵社上班。//<a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E4%B8%9C%E5%9C%9F%E5%A4%A7%E5%94%90%E4%B8%89%E4%BF%97%E5%92%8C%E5%B0%9A?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">@东土大唐三俗和尚</a>: 文学造旨已经到了莫名其抄的地步！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1699972153\" target=\"_blank\">飞上云端了</a>：段子：有一句常挂嘴边的台词：国内外敌对势力亡我之心不死！请记住，那个“我”只指朝廷的既得利益者，并不包括你！有不少奴才一厢情愿地把自己归纳到“我”字当中，就象古时候的太监一厢情愿地把自己归纳为皇室成员一样。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2837873344\" target=\"_blank\">Vanessa的呼吸</a>：D需要的是听话的狗，出些笑话很正常，这次不是又提升了两个笑话。。。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1527318174\" target=\"_blank\">整合之道刘鸿雁</a>：“花式修辞”与“臭带鱼效应”？<img title=\"[酷]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/40/cool_org.gif\" alt=\"[酷]\" /><img title=\"[思考]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/e9/sk_org.gif\" alt=\"[思考]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/n/%E5%8F%AA%E9%85%8D%E5%8F%AB%E7%8C%AA?from=feed&amp;loc=at\" target=\"_blank\">只配叫猪</a>: 近来宣传战线人才辈出局面大好。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1949554930\" target=\"_blank\">还是居士</a>：萱萱系统逆淘汰，已经到了这个份上了，可喜可贺。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/5035754373\" target=\"_blank\">晏轻yq</a>：一代不如一代；高层正能量己足够荒唐了；下面还在荒唐；气死张春桥姚文元了；你们拍马吹牛都不会了！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/lizuoy\" target=\"_blank\">草堂评说</a>：街头巷尾无处不在的那些宣传广告：1、花的是民脂民膏；2、洗的是百姓大脑；3、美化的是当权者；4、肥了当事人的腰包！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/busizhimi\" target=\"_blank\">不死之謎外傳</a>：我是佩服的五体投地。没有他们，会有这么多顺民吗？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/2273170580\" target=\"_blank\">八斗愚公</a>：俺的梦想：恢复帝制！封建帝制在天朝经过数千年的反复实践日渐成熟，既有经验又有基础，水到渠成，不需盲人瞎马摸石头过河，担惊受怕。<img title=\"[哈哈]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6a/laugh.gif\" alt=\"[哈哈]\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/1421788025\" target=\"_blank\">壬申壬午</a>：神州树树花千芳，庆丰包包周带鱼！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/yangchentao\" target=\"_blank\">不做沉默的大多数</a>：我党宣传系统的丰功伟绩真是罄竹难书！</p>\n<p>【网络民议系列为中国数字时代特色原创内容，如需转载请遵守本站采用Creative Commons 的 Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0 协议。】</p>\n","author":1019,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016],"tags":[26000,9000,24505,21038,13999,26006,27354]}